primefactr
  • Reference

Get all prime numbers.

Get all prime numbers up to n.

AllPrimesUpTo(n)

Arguments

n
A positive integer.

Value

A integer vector of all prime numbers up to n.

Examples

AllPrimesUpTo(10)
#> [1] 2 3 5 7
AllPrimesUpTo(100)
